FAQs
What programs are offered at Tbilisi State Medical University?

TSMU offers undergraduate and postgraduate programs in medicine, dentistry, and pharmacy, along with various research opportunities.

Is the degree from TSMU recognized internationally?

Yes, degrees from TSMU are recognized by major medical councils and organizations worldwide, including WHO and MCI.

How can Qadri-International assist in the application process?

Qadri-International provides personalized counseling, application assistance, and support with visa applications and pre-departure preparations.

What is the cost of living in Tbilisi for students?

Tbilisi offers an affordable cost of living compared to other European cities, with reasonably priced accommodation, dining, and transportation options.

